You have the following rights in relation to your data, which you can exercise at any time:

    the right to access your stored personal data;
    the right to rectify, block or erase your personal data, or to have incomplete data completed (if due to legal storage obligations we can only erase your data at a later date, they will be blocked in the meantime);
    the right to delete your customer account or to arrange for it to be deleted;
